# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Repo-specific exclusions
# This repo is for Optimizely Solutions Architects + engineering — we publish
# code, enhancements, and fixes for Optimizely Edge Delivery. The following are
# NOT shared:
#   - Customer-named research and reports (AmeriSave engagement materials)
#   - Local recovery / backup directories
#   - macOS "* copy.*" restoration duplicates
#   - Past validation run output JSON
#   - Old/superseded README and nested scratch copies
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Customer-named research and reports
amerisave/
CUSTOMER-REPORT-AMERISAVE.md
FINAL-REPORT-AMERISAVE.md
ENGINEERING-REPORT-304-BLANK-PAGE-FIX.md
ENGINEERING-REPORT-STALE-REVISION.md

# Customer reply drafts (not pushed — internal communication staging)
_customer-replies/
**/_customer-replies/
CUSTOMER-REPLY-*.md
**/CUSTOMER-REPLY-*.md

# Local recovery backup of edge-del-v2 (same content; do not push)
edge-del-v2-recovered/

# Restore duplicates (Finder-style "<name> copy.<ext>")
* copy.md
* copy.js
* copy.ts
* copy.mjs
* copy.json
* copy.txt
* copy/
**/* copy.md
**/* copy.js
**/* copy.ts
**/* copy.mjs
**/* copy.json
**/* copy.txt
**/* copy/

# Past validation run outputs (timestamped output, regenerable)
edge-validation-report.json
fix-verification-report.json
soak-report.json

# Old/superseded
validation-README.md

# Nested scratch copy (recursive container)
___temp_research/
